data.title: KL SENTRAL RAILWAY STATION
data.meta_description:
24 reviews and 34 photos of KL SENTRAL RAILWAY STATION "An interchange station for buses, KTMs, LRT Kelana Jaya and Monorails. Almost all in one (almost because LRT STAR Ampang doesn't included here -LOL) Most of the time, this station will be pack with the crowd, as there's many fast food restaurants such as KFC and McD, convenience shops like 7-Eleven, News, there's even Guardian here!

Plus, there's another brand new open shopping mall : NU Central which make the crowd becomes even more. But worry less, the service here are tip top! (except maybe for KFC and McD because of too many people!) Everything else - buying the tickets, reloading your TNG/Rapid, wait and getting into the trains (except KTM - lols) , everything here is fast!

Well, I always come here by trains, so I'm not so sure about car parking here. Hope this will help at least a little bit!

Operating hours:  6.00am - 12.30am"
data.text:
“Located at strategic place, KL sentral become a transit for KLIA express, KTM , Rapid KL, and also Monorail.” in 9 reviews

“It is the central transportation hub for this city as the KTM, LRT and KLIA Ekspres/Transit train services all have stops at this station.” in 10 reviews
